        <abstract> 
<p>Sends his translation of Wallace’s <hi rend="italic">Malay Archipelago</hi>.</p>  
<p>Wishes to translate 1858 essays by CD and Wallace from Linnean Society <hi rend="italic">Proceedings</hi> [<hi rend="italic">Collected papers</hi> 2: 3–19].</p> 
            <p>Plans journey to tropics.</p>
            <p>Hopes to meet CD.</p>
        </abstract>
